{"tid":781975,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"(終結世界大戰)Inception 結局終於有答案","createTime":"2018-08-16T10:36:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-18T14:11:13.000Z","uid":98659,"like":21,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"54e12e389189112e2a047ec37ffca98cc0946dae","tid":781975,"uid":98659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T10:36:36.000Z","msg":"相信任何對Christopher Nolan的介紹都是多餘，由Momento到Dark Knight到Dunkirk，他早已用自己的作品向世人介紹自己。而在2010年的Inception除了令大家在視覺效果上睇到嘩嘩聲之外，夢中夢中夢的結構應令人對結局Leonardo Dicaprio身在何方一直疑問。雖然Nolan本人在以前就曾作答，但模稜兩可的答案卻未能滿足戲迷。結果，屬於Nolan御用的英國國寶級演員Michael Caine終於就問題釋法，一鎚定音。<br />\n<br />\n簡而言之，Michael Caine提供的答案是Leo所演的Cobb在結局經已回到現實。<br />\n<br />\n事源是Caine出席Film4 Summer Screen室外放映活動，負責介紹Nolan的電影時終於說出答案。因為Nolan曾向他解釋，只要該幕戲有Caine的參與，即為現實。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.firstpost.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Caine-Inception-825.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.firstpost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2FCaine-Inception-825.jpg&h=9e0f1f26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://men.fanpiece.com/mensuno/Inception-%E7%B5%90%E5%B1%80%E7%B5%82%E6%96%BC%E6%9C%89%E7%AD%94%E6%A1%88-Michael-Caine-%E4%B8%80%E9%8E%9A%E5%AE%9A%E9%9F%B3-c1327620.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmen.fanpiece.com%2Fmensuno%2FInception-%25E7%25B5%2590%25E5%25B1%2580%25E7%25B5%2582%25E6%2596%25BC%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%25AD%2594%25E6%25A1%2588-Michael-Caine-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E9%258E%259A%25E5%25AE%259A%25E9%259F%25B3-c1327620.html&d=Pl9Y0NndIBa%2F5fkSG1v2xZUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=cc9d8e88\" target=\"_blank\">https://men.fanpiece.com/mensuno/Inception-%E7%B5%90%E5%B1%80%E7%B5%82%E6%96%BC%E6%9C%89%E7%AD%94%E6%A1%88-Michael-Caine-%E4%B8%80%E9%8E%9A%E5%AE%9A%E9%9F%B3-c1327620.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n終於睇得明套戲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef8ddddfcd337a9214315057b3df30037f9497af","tid":781975,"uid":4826,"like"